      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of May 9 article on Tony Award nominations; Michael Mayer was director with most recent multiple nominations in different categories</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article yesterday about the Tony Award nominations referred incorrectly to the previous occurrence of multiple nominations for a single director in different categories. Michael Blakemore, with two such nominations this year, was similarly nominated 10 years ago, but the most recent case was that of Michael Mayer, nominated last year for both the musical ''You're a Good Man, Charlie Brown'' and the play ''Side Man.''</p>
      </block>
